Directed by Ron Howard (Apollo 13, The Da Vinci Code)

Eternal, classic Science Fiction with a heart and lots of laughs, where the senior citizens in a small town are revitalized by extraterrestial energies. Hard to forget the &#039;cosmic orgasm&#039; given to Steve Guttenberg in a swimmingpool by alien Tahnee Welch (daughter of Raquel).

One of the last performances for the whole class of Hollywood oldtimers like Don Ameche (Oscar), Jessica Tandy, Hume Cronyn and Wilford Brimley.

DVDrip, Widescreen 704x368, 2-pass, great stereo AC3.
Burn tested, runs well in both my standalone DivX players.
